column1: Data description: Scores from principal component analyses of grassland species traits with and without annual grasses
Names of data takers: Analyzed by Barbara Fernandez-Going
Column info: Site (1-80), PC1 and PC2 with annual grasses, PC1 and PC2 without annual grasses
Definitions & Abbreviations: PC1=principal component axis 1, PC2= principal component axis 2, ag=with annual grasses, noag=without annual grasses
